{"tid":1905714,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】深圳書城未見《大國戰「疫」》 疑拍馬屁惹眾怒被下架","createTime":"2020-03-01T12:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T12:33:19.000Z","uid":41343,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9096375ae12e9b26c963d86a1e0cd7249f55f20e","tid":1905714,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:27:07.000Z","msg":"（新增內容）中共吹噓在武漢肺炎的抗疫工作，不惜在疫情仍未完全受控下，急急出版圖書《大國戰「疫」&mdash;&mdash;2020中國阻擊新冠肺炎疫情進行中》（下稱：《大國戰「疫」》），一邊為中國打造成「抗疫英雄」，又繼續為習近平的管治「貼金」。可是，這書出版後即時受到各界狠批，淘寶網疑為免民情反彈，近日已將這本書下架。<br />\n<br />\n從網民截圖中看到，淘寶天貓的中信書店，《大國戰「疫」》已被註明「暫無報價」，淘寶其他書店，亦無法找到《大國戰「疫」》的貨源。<br />\n<br />\n今日在深圳書城，展示新書的枱面放置多本與疫情有關的圖書，《鍾南山談健康》等醫健類新書擺放在顯眼位置，惟並沒有此前新華社預告即將出版的《大國戰「疫」》，而在擺放習近平著作的專櫃，亦不見這本書。<br />\n<br />\n内地傳媒人指，《大國戰「疫」》已在各大購書網全線下架，暫停預售，原因未明。雖然是星期日，但深圳南山書城在疫情下人流甚少，内裏的咖啡店、國畫藝術店和少兒美術培訓室等全部暫停營業。與平常假日書客熙來攘往比較，人流僅餘一成不到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《大國戰「疫」》由中宣部、國務院新聞辦公室指導，五洲傳播出版社和人民出版社聯合製作。疫情未遏情況上，中共就出版該書，即被無數網民批評是「拍馬屁」、「臉皮比地殼還厚」。<br />\n<br />\n綜合報道"},{"pid":"5fdbda36a0b091bdc45836dd8c6e50eb1e4c9adc","tid":1905714,"uid":36134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:29:01.000Z","msg":"刁帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249aea5b1f0863012408f46981c321c48b4d0726","tid":1905714,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:29:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200301/JS7JBARUJHKMQ2MCXXVDBBVS4E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200301%2FJS7JBARUJHKMQ2MCXXVDBBVS4E%2F&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGoje9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=3858de99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200301%2FJS7JBARUJHKMQ2MCXXVDBBVS4E%2F&h=65cfb5db\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200301/JS7JBARUJHKMQ2MCXXVDBBVS4E/</a>"},{"pid":"abba1590e875a13d165f6a929426ee29586a70cc","tid":1905714,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:30:00.000Z","msg":"仲得閒寫書<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8afabddd86e1d094df5b06f2548fac0dc6381060","tid":1905714,"uid":222238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"abba1590e875a13d165f6a929426ee29586a70cc","tid":1905714,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:30:00.000Z","msg":"仲得閒寫書<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:31:16.000Z","msg":"中左肺炎要隔離, 得閒到親自寫書"},{"pid":"86d2442dafde35024b08b3fefa49104aae40a882","tid":1905714,"uid":265499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:33:17.000Z","msg":"我親自下架"},{"pid":"617d8490a2445015dd0eb27dedd10582bc3dfd6f","tid":1905714,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8afabddd86e1d094df5b06f2548fac0dc6381060","tid":1905714,"uid":222238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"abba1590e875a13d165f6a929426ee29586a70cc","tid":1905714,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:30:00.000Z","msg":"仲得閒寫書<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:31:16.000Z","msg":"中左肺炎要隔離, 得閒到親自寫書"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:33:19.000Z","msg":"條小學生自己可能連睇都未睇過啊"}]}